00:51:12,324 --> 00:51:13,655
Like that:

784
00:51:13,859 --> 00:51:16,453
You can see the star,
you can't see the planet.

785
00:51:16,662 --> 00:51:19,028
So now I'm gonna need two volunteers.

786
00:51:21,233 --> 00:51:22,257
You two.

787
00:51:23,602 --> 00:51:26,469
Just to save time
because they're in the front row.

788
00:51:26,672 --> 00:51:29,698
I need one of you to turn
the star and the planet...

789
00:51:29,909 --> 00:51:33,868
...and another person to pull
