790
00:51:34,079 --> 00:51:35,546
And what you will see...

791
00:51:35,748 --> 00:51:39,081
...is that the star
you can make out...

792
00:51:39,285 --> 00:51:41,913
...will be moving
in a funny, wiggly pattern...

793
00:51:42,121 --> 00:51:44,248
...which will be the clue,
the evidence...

794
00:51:44,456 --> 00:51:46,720
...for the existence
