867
00:55:57,509 --> 00:56:01,275
We make our world significant by
the courage of our questions...

868
00:56:01,713 --> 00:56:04,341
...and by the depth of our answers.

869
00:56:05,918 --> 00:56:09,012
We embarked on our journey
to the stars...

870
00:56:09,621 --> 00:56:12,215
...with a question first framed...

871
00:56:12,424 --> 00:56:14,949
...in the childhood of our species...

872
00:56:15,394 --> 00:56:19,660
...and in each generation
asked anew...

873
00:56:19,932 --> 00:56:22,093
...with undiminished wonder:

874
00:56:22,467 --> 00:56:24,628
"What are the stars?"

875
00:56:42,721 --> 00:56:45,588
Exploration is in our nature.

876
00:56:46,191 --> 00:56:48,489
We began as wanderers...

877
00:56:48,794 --> 00:56:51,661
...and we are wanderers still.

878
00:57:02,941 --> 00:57:05,637
We have lingered long enough...

879
00:57:05,844 --> 00:57:08,642
